This paper is primarily focused on predicting insider threats in the context of information security, which falls under the category of "Computer and Information Science" (cs.CR). The paper also extensively uses machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be classified under "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses pre-processing of organizational log data, which could be classified under "Software Engineering" (cs.SE). Finally, the paper deals with security and privacy concerns, which could be classified under "Cryptography and Security" (cs.CY).
